org.synchronoss.cpo

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.synchronoss.cpo.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Node>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BindableCpoWhere

    public class Node
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Node>
    This is a general Node class to be used to build different types of trees. There are very few rules in this class as they should be implemented by users of this class.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    David E. Berry
